### AxumWithRust.http ### This file contains HTTP requests for testing an Axum server built with Rust.
### Variables @baseUrl = http://localhost:5000 @contentType = application/json
### GET request to root endpoint GET {{baseUrl}}/
### GET request with query parameters GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10
### GET request with headers GET {{baseUrl}}/protected Authorization: Bearer your-token-here Accept: application/json
### POST request with JSON body POST {{baseUrl}}/users Content-Type: {{contentType}}
{ "name": "John Doe", "email": "john@example.com", "age": 30 }
